value.0: This flightless, domesticated bird is prized both for its tender meat and for the eggs it lays on an almost daily basis. This one doesn't appear timid nor perky though.
This appears to be a mug, which can be filled to the brim with whatever drink is your personal choice.  Great for souveneirs from your favorite pub.

Value.value: We seem to have a slight problem with reaching the Monolith. Our organisation is doing its best to guarantee the quality of your trip.
I quote our disclaimer: "8b. It is extremely important that you realize that, for boat trips, the operator takes no responsibility at all."
No, you won't get a refund. For a modest fee we will be happy to ship you to a destination of your choice, of course.
